            <h3>Establishment in the Eastern Province</h3>
            <p>The business was established in 1940 in the Eastern Province. In its early commercial history, the Company is known for establishing the first warehouse dedicated solely to Saudi Aramco and for supplying Saudi Aramco's first locally purchased order for steel pipes, tugboats, and tires.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item tl-year-right">
          <div class="timeline-content reveal">
            <h3>Early Industrial Development</h3>
            <p>The group's historical profile also records its role in early industrial development in the Eastern Province, including the first electric power station and the Saudi cement plant.</p>
